 response by 8PM today (2 August 2019).<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFC2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=5f58950a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"ea92c8b9c6c8032cda9b380d893780933bd0ad0c","tid":1395470,"uid":143481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"786abcbd63ec68432255311e2f33a19c985dfb7c","tid":1395470,"uid":157042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"支持你落現場前線義士講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2839fe7d79b0706d99a0ea1e1954709bd62491","tid":1395470,"uid":189015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:42:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n下次被人影時唔需要咁緊張，語氣好D咁叫人del相啦"},{"pid":"f4c7247241af8227794c0367a45aef37aa35966f","tid":1395470,"uid":157042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"786abcbd63ec68432255311e2f33a19c985dfb7c","tid":1395470,"uid":157042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"支持你落現場前線義士講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"同義士講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97b9850444a46c2c17b695747f7919dc5bcdca8","tid":1395470,"uid":143481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"786abcbd63ec68432255311e2f33a19c985dfb7c","tid":1395470,"uid":157042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"